STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Walter A. TORMASI, Defendant-Petitioner. C-869 September Term 2018
082098 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 3, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004261-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied; and it is further

ORDERED that the notice of appeal is dismissed.
